{"tid":237879,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶)中國潮興吃特色菜「地雷」　重慶女不慎爆炸受傷","createTime":"2017-05-10T16:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T17:14:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a253ca6e4cde2bfe68c0e3586194a373e394a4ce","tid":237879,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/photo/bkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170312172805\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170312172805&h=fbbf0cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">陳女（箭嘴示）跟同學飯聚時，特色菜「地雷」發生爆炸，遭裝置碎片及熱湯燙傷。（網上圖片）</span><br />\n中國有一道名為「地雷」的特色菜，餸菜裝在一個酷似「地雷」的裝置內，食客進食前需點燃設在裝置的引線，裝置便會打開。重慶沙坪壩區一名陳姓女子昨日跟舊同學飯聚，也點了這道菜，沒料她在點燃「地雷」後，「地雷」果真「爆炸」，餸菜的熱湯及裝置碎片炸飛，致陳臉部燙傷。經協調後，餐廳老闆向陳女賠償500元（人民幣‧下同）作檢查治療費用。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚陳女跟高中同學到涉事餐廳飯聚，眾人經侍應推薦，點了特色菜「地雷」。上菜後，陳女等人按侍應指示，點燃「地雷裝置」的引線，未料裝置瞬間發生爆炸，裝置的碎片及餸菜燙熱的湯汁飛濺出來，致陳女臉部受傷，其羽絨被燒了幾個窟窿。<br />\n<br />\n意外後，陳女等人找餐廳老闆協商處理事件，惟溝通期間陳等人認為侍應態度不佳，於是報警求助。警方到場了解並查看陳女傷勢，發現其臉部傷勢並不算嚴重。經警方調解，餐廳老闆向陳女及其同學賠禮道歉，並支付陳女500元檢查治療費，雙方達成和解。<br />\n<br />\n另針對餐館在管理中存在的安全問題，警員亦當場提出整改建議，餐廳老闆亦答應立即進行整改，及對員工進行教育培訓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/photo/bkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_02b.jpg?20170312172805\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20170312172805&h=4f45f077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食客點燃「地雷」裝置的引線後，裝置便會炸開。（網上圖片<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/bkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170312%2Fbkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001.html&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=100bded3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170312/bkncn-20170312152915011-0312_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"afbb9e418f77be489461a637c1cd55e3c38e4239","tid":237879,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"中國製地雷終於識爆<br />\n崛起了🚬"},{"pid":"1073d5c0c7048ce5b2f3a9a37223a3ef1ced5ea9","tid":237879,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qpvwlakz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqpvwlakz&h=7df1d441&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a34cd446ba3ed3c91af07586680b868f1d46cec","tid":237879,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photocdn.sohu.com/20170304/Img482357454.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotocdn.sohu.com%2F20170304%2FImg482357454.gif&h=a1cfe49b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/144397/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/144397/page/1?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"f28a6d23fc17d3e0b1028719ee3a46280c789791","tid":237879,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"屌你黎返去cc台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ff84d48d9d266b8b52bed023f9e8c75ade8e6e","tid":237879,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e332e3ba8ccafb78568dd552532021714644776b","tid":237879,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:14:10.000Z","msg":"食神早已發明"}]}